arts.ttl: Euro 2025: Sweden eases past Poland and advances to quarterfinals along with Germany
arts.sum: Sweden has advanced to the quarterfinals at the Women’s European Championship by beating Poland 3-0.

Minute-by-minute updates on the action in Lucerne Email Niall | Player guide | Germany 2-1 Denmark 2 mins: Sweden hit the bar! Asllani gets her head to a deflected cross and her effort loops onto the crossbar. Poland get it clear, but not for long … 1 min: Madelen Janogy, who’s started the first two games with Fridolina Rolfo recovering from injury, gets away down the left. Her cross is cleared at the near post, and the winger can’t steer the rebound on target. Continue reading...
